Package veslo

Class AllureCallAdapterFactory

java.lang.Object
retrofit2.CallAdapter.Factory
veslo.client.adapter.JavaTypeCallAdapterFactory
veslo.client.adapter.UniversalCallAdapterFactory
veslo.AllureCallAdapterFactory
public class AllureCallAdapterFactory
extends UniversalCallAdapterFactory
Factory for creating CallAdapter with support for Allure steps. Overridden methods: - getEndpointInfo() - get call info from allure Description annotation - getCallAdapter() - wrapped in Allure step API call.

Author:
Oleg Shaburov (shaburov.o.a@gmail.com) Created: 01.12.2021
